# ❌ Subscription Cancel App
A smart tool that helps you track, manage, and cancel unwanted subscriptions — 
so you stop losing money on services you don't use.

## 🎯 Who It's For
Small business owners, entrepreneurs, and individuals who want to take control 
of their recurring expenses.

## ✨ Features
- Track active subscriptions in one place
- Identify subscriptions to cancel
- Save money by cutting unused services

